A '''time-lock device''' was a device required on all spaceship docks by [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] [[Imperial Order D6-66/Legends|Order D6-66]]. They were used by spaceship docks, Imperial officials and Spaceship Owners to lock down their ship for a certain amount of time. This was used for impounding ships and securing them.

